Welcome to the=C2=A01,097=C2=A0newly Not Boring people=C2=A0who have joined=
 us over the past two weeks! If you haven=E2=80=99t subscribed, join=C2=A02=
03,901 smart, curious folks by subscribing here:
Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,=C2=A0
Happy Monday! Grab a coffee, shake off the weekend, and let=E2=80=99s talk =
fusion.=C2=A0
Energy is upstream of everything we write about here at Not Boring. Cheap, =
abundant energy means economic prosperity, sci-fi brought to life, and even=
, one day, flying cars. So when Helion announced that it planned to deliver=
 commercial fusion power in 2028, our ears perked up.=C2=A0
Luckily, we=E2=80=99d been working on a fusion piece. Rahul Rana [ https://=
substack.com/redirect/c94964b8-6835-495f-aee4-b8b5293b9a55?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAw=
Z3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] (who graduated from Ru=
tgers last weekend [ https://substack.com/redirect/e7d28724-4080-4706-8efd-=
b8b46ebf9562?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8Exk=
RNpU ] =E2=80=93 congrats Rahul!!) is both a student of the history of moon=
shot [ https://substack.com/redirect/7008d925-39f7-4727-8e3f-7fb558cfa2bd?j=
=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] project=
s in the United States and smart enough to understand and break down everyt=
hing going on in the world of fusion.=C2=A0
So we decided to team up on a piece explaining how fusion works, where we a=
re in our progress towards commercial-scale fusion, and why the transition =
from government-funded to private sector should spell acceleration.=C2=A0
We are certainly not experts on fusion. Treat this as a ride-along as we le=
arn about the science and history of fusion, where it stands today, and whe=
re we might be headed in the coming years, complete with an overview of som=
e of the most promising fusion startups.=C2=A0It=E2=80=99s a topic we expec=
t we=E2=80=99ll hear about and cover a lot more in the years ahead.
Whether 2028 is realistic or not, the Fusion Race is on. This piece is mean=
t to be your starting point on one of the next decade=E2=80=99s most import=
ant adventures.=C2=A0Read on or click here to jump to the full version onli=
ne [ https://substack.com/redirect/890ab582-c800-4254-a045-40ae974c651f?j=
=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
