ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So we decided to team up =
on a piece explaining how fusion works, where we are in our progress toward=
s commercial-scale fusion, and why the transition from government-funded to=
 private sector should spell acceleration.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #404=
040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">We are certai=
nly not experts on fusion. Treat this as a ride-along as we learn about the=
