">bidirectional</a><span> relationship between energy consumption and econo=
mic growth. </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/2cb39cde-fa4c-4=
c3c-b3ad-365c7d96fc20?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOs=
a8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">Re=
searchers found</a><span> that a 1% increase in real GDP per capita increas=
es total energy consumption by 0.6%. </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com=
